{"tid":579270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【虎熊大戰】虎爪勁猛熊掌深沉 鹿死誰手未可知","createTime":"2018-03-03T12:27:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-03T12:56:46.000Z","uid":3393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"09e4b08cb1c5c576dcf05a6dc3eb6568010c258f","tid":579270,"uid":3393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T12:27:04.000Z","msg":"在印度馬哈拉施特拉邦(Maharashtra)的塔杜巴國家公園(Tadoba National Park)，上演了一場虎熊大戰，雙方拳拳到肉，均有爭勝雄心，過程精彩萬分。<br />\n<br />\n一開始時，該頭兇猛的成年老虎佔盡上風，把行動遲緩的黑熊按在地上，用虎爪夾著牠的頸。<br />\n<br />\n黑熊看似要落敗，但憑著不屈不撓的精神，牠最後擺脫猛虎的糾纏，後腿站起，勇猛地擋格老虎的攻擊。老虎見久攻不下，又拿不到甚麼甜頭，終無奈停戰離開，雙方可說打成平手。<br />\n<br />\n美國《紐約郵報》  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180303/57897566\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180303%2F57897566&d=pu1QnqsHZMSH7oFri48CKwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=f1c3e84c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180303%2F57897566&h=c2d08a5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180303/57897566</a>"},{"pid":"bc72cf21223eac48e2f2b1bcf1c08ca70910fc1a","tid":579270,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T12:35:28.000Z","msg":"鹿呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df6771986704264683b6dd5c84aeeb0cc0f997d","tid":579270,"uid":11962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T12:45:30.000Z","msg":"打隻熊BB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ca049e56a46c62c7a9187602b9f0babde38ad2","tid":579270,"uid":26752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T12:47:30.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打和supper<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>